About this school

Dodge Co Primary School is a town public school in Eastman, Georgia that is part of Dodge County School District. It serves 300 students in Pre-K - 2 with a student/teacher ratio of 5.6:1. Its teachers have had 8 projects funded on DonorsChoose.
